### <a name="does-the-location-of-your-customer-data-have-a-direct-impact-on-your-end-users-experience"></a><span data-ttu-id="8233e-124">O local dos dados de seus clientes afeta diretamente a experiência dos usuários finais?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8233e-124">Does the location of your customer data have a direct impact on your end users' experience?</span></span>
